glosses.gloss: Abolitionism or abolitionist veganism is the animal rights based opposition to all animal use by humans.
The movement to end the property status of animals
해방주의란 동물권 운동가 사이의 이론으로 동물을 소유의 객체가 아니라 해방의 대상으로 생각의 전환을 주장하는 이론이다.
The doctrine that calls for the abolition of slavery
Abolitionism is a general term which describes the movement to end slavery.
Movement to end slavery
Opposition to slavery.
Person who is opposed to slavery.
The doctrine that calls for the abolition of slavery.
The campaign against the abolition of the slave trade and/or slavery.
An opinion in favor of the abolition of something; the tenets of abolitionists.
Opinion in favor of the abolition of something.
Abolitionism is a political movement that seeks to abolish the practice of slavery and the worldwide slave trade.
노예제 폐지운동은 19세기에 서유럽과 미국에서 노예 제도의 폐지를 목적으로 전개된 인도주의적 개혁 운동이다.
Putting a condemned person to death
Capital punishment, also known as the death penalty, is a government-sanctioned practice whereby a person is put to death by the state as a punishment for a crime.
The act of the state putting a person to death
Legal process whereby a person is put to death by the state as a punishment for a crime. Use as value for "manner of death" (P1196)
The judicially ordered execution of a person as a punishment for a serious crime.
The act of commiting capital punishment against someone for a certain crime or action
A punishment in which the offender is put to death by the state.
The practice of putting a person to death as a punishment for a crime.
The act of putting to death or being put to death as a penalty, or actions so associated.
Any crime that is punishable by death.
State punishment of death.
Capital punishment, also known as the death penalty, is the execution of a convicted criminal by the state as punishment for crimes known as capital crimes or capital offences.
사형은 사람의 생명을 박탈하는 형벌로, 생명형 또는 극형이라고도 한다.
공개 처형은 대중이 모이는 장소에서 사형 집행을 하거나 사형 집행 장면을 공개하는 것을 의미한다.
범죄자 혹은 범죄자라고 주장되는 사람의 생명을 박탈하여 사회에서 영원히 격리시키는 형벌이다.
